Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.71,0:02:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九十三話\N敵人在戰場原  追求翡翠的紋章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.18,0:02:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(咒)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.86,0:02:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一個禮拜你不能起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一天分三次 一次喝一點泉水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.77,0:03:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟陣風要趕到日光去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.48,0:03:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好\N龍脈到達日光還需要時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.22,0:03:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先繞過去找出\N將龍脈方向調向府內的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.79,0:03:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它摧毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.59,0:03:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼摧毀？怎麼阻止？\N那麼可怕的東西的動向…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.86,0:03:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.43,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔 你是風水師吧\N應該知道什麼方法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.84,0:03:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是沒有辦法 只是…\N不瞭解敵人的動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也很難行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始你怎麼不講清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.48,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 月岡\N我想順便拜託你們一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.52,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是搶陣地遊戲嗎？\N這個太簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.52,0:03:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風想知道靈水他們是\N在日光的哪裏改變龍脈方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此 還需要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.57,0:04:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是抱著什麼目的\N把龍脈撞向府內的什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是想請你調查這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我試試看 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相會地點是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該在日光的某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.15,0:04:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時我們跟他們\N應該會惹出不小的騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.09,0:04:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去準備旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 不可以丟下阿薰一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水…水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去跟鄰居要水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.55,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.26,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經塗上泉水了\N沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.07,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風 你認為靈水他們\N可能在日光的哪裏設陣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.87,0:05:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最有可能的地方是東照宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是祭祀德川家康的靈廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多風水機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.22,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是代代相傳的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.19,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日光東照宮有隱藏\N德川家康留下的翡翠紋章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翡翠紋章？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.26,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.16,0:05:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以自由自在\N控制所有強力氣脈的紋章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.54,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果傳說是真的\N也許可以阻止那個氣脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.61,0:05:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水之族沒有為德川家康所用\N所以不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是只有風之族才知道的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川的時代已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們至今\N仍被過去的亡靈給擺佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 快到外面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太政官命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.71,0:07:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請閣下暫時閉門思過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.71,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼\N這種緊急時候你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.58,0:07:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是太政官命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閣下自作主張將近衛大隊\N派往武藏野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且未經准許就封鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太政官管理下的\N民營企業的工地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我陪您到貴府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.07,0:07:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閣下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.71,0:07:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切責任都在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 遷出這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把所有可能\N落為證據的東西全部燒燬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水大人已經開始\N操作龍脈的儀式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幽水大人\N請與我們趕去日光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我可以下命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.82,0:08:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能再前進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有話問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該說的我全跟警方說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是普通的辦事員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的全部講了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的 三個月前左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就收到佐伯社長奇怪的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼奇怪法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要我調查府內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.36,0:09:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由北方的赤羽到\N元老院之間的所有神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從赤羽到元老院？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 特別是裹鬼門的數目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為是社長命令的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.97,0:09:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想對警方而言\N這種細節無關緊要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就沒說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子你還知道更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我沒隱瞞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要我去找太政官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿七年前\N神佛分離令時候的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我動用很多方法 總算…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元老院跟神佛分離令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有看到資料嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家有手抄本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.43,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（咒）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.37,0:10:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是警視廳的川路先生\N我們也不能讓你進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.07,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少答應我解開\N對山縣大人的軟禁懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 太政官到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種非常時刻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.48,0:11:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不提那個 明天下午\N一點的聚會沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元老院呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不光是大臣、參議員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.76,0:11:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是連日本各地縣令\N都會聚集過來的大聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有閒時待在這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 署長 我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.81,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戒備 加強府內的戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現可疑人物就抓起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你說的沒錯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 是你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.52,0:11:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯調查府內神社\N所有裹鬼門的數目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.66,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈通過裹鬼門時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那威力會大幅提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們打算讓龍脈\N撞上最終目標呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.33,0:11:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說明天的聚會是下午一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.97,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜那是他們動手的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終目標是元老院嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.76,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.83,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說是機關\N連他們的蹤影都沒看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這後面是東照宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面的院子\N就是德川家康的墳墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要改變龍脈的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要大規模的五芒星之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.76,0:12:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個靈廟…\N一定被加入那個魔法陣之中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼什麼機關也沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.87,0:13:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風\N現在以尋找翡翠紋章為優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管靈水使出什麼計策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.48,0:13:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有那個紋章\N就能與他對搞了不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.35,0:13:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 我想馬上去日光耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.65,0:13:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很介意那個神佛分離令\N等確認完之後再走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.13,0:13:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 突然造訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫月岡津南 出版社的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件事想請問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 你是在哪裏得到這個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.61,0:13:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 我沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,容我馬上進入正題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.05,0:13:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是七年前政府發佈\N神佛分離令時的機密資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.12,0:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們完全\N看不懂上面寫了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,資料的最後 署名的執筆者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.32,0:13:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堀中正 那是你吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託 告訴我內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 這確實是我的著作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒時間了 老爺子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很性急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.87,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是分割日光東照宮的細節紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.44,0:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府害怕東照宮的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要德川家康的靈廟尚存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.82,0:14:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川的亡靈們\N可能再度行動呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.39,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以把東照宮的一些機關\N移動到別的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中還有可以自由控制\N地底氣脈的機關呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.50,0:14:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個特別受到重視\N被劃入極機密資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.68,0:14:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要埋掉那個大東西很辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.01,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,埋？埋在哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰場原呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰場原…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.85,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個機關等於兩刃劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用法不當 搞不好會滅國呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.36,0:15:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 要啟動它\N還需要翡翠紋章呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紋章被置入陽明門的欄杆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陽明門？那麼顯眼的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.07,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想節儉成性的德川家康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.71,0:15:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祭祀他的靈廟中為何有\N那麼壯大華麗的門呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.12,0:15:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說為了隱藏翡翠紋章\N故意做華麗的裝飾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.09,0:15:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道以後只能夠看他們了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 應該還有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.57,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜線索在這裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下來的只有這個陽明門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.47,0:16:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風 那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個徽章都很舊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有那個 看來跟新的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幽水還沒到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.05,0:16:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個人已經進入東照宮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.09,0:16:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 現在已經\N沒有阻止龍脈的方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.00,0:16:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧 既然他們急著找死\N我就如他們所願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.07,0:16:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為我們水之族達成心願\N來個錦上添花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頑！滅！殺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是大陸風水 玉座之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玉座之陣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是靈水的幻術？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.59,0:17:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好了 設在靈廟的\N玉座之陣像鋼牆鐵壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.26,0:17:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我能做的\N只有減弱他送進來的邪氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的只能靠你\N自己的意志力來渡過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退！弱！清！淨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.44,0:18:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道要我跟自己搏鬥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退！弱！清！淨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.73,0:18:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退！弱！清！淨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退！弱！清！淨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退！弱！清！淨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…還有人等著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果在這裏被打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多無辜的人們會死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越是勉強想切斷過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越是會受到幻影撥弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這恐怕是大陸風水的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與過去共同並存的覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是現在我的最大武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被破解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.74,0:19:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正這只是項餘興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.38,0:19:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓明天的大業完成就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.19,0:19:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打贏了以自己的心為巢穴的幻影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.19,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都多虧陣風你\N削弱了玉座之陣的邪氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是仿冒品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翡翠紋章一定在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.24,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.94,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 查出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可是禍不單行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.71,0:19:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水的目標是元老院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一點\N叫做翡翠紋章那東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投降了 我這外行人\N看了就一團混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那倒未必 我漸漸看懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.13,0:20:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是江戶守護結界的解體紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.07,0:20:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反過來看\N就成為守護結界的組合式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.47,0:20:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,江戶的中心是江戶城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以本丸為基點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艮的方位是上野、淺草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.04,0:20:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一帶應該是\N被足以與東照宮匹敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.85,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈力強大的神社或佛寺守護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個神社是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.12,0:20:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該在這裏\N仿照守護京都鬼門的比壑山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有東壑山的山號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.66,0:20:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與東照宮一樣\N由天海大和尚建立的寬永寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寬永寺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏在六年前的上野戰爭中\N幾乎化為一片焦土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來…那也在他們計算中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.74,0:20:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.84,0:20:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在注意到也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到\N維新的爪子會伸到這個區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂…這裏禁止平民進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.79,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘記告訴二位一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我一個忙好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.36,0:21:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 五芒星的點\N各自分佈在東照宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.03,0:21:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二荒山神社、輪王寺\N龍王瀑布、以及男體山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.44,0:21:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這五個陣互相發揮作用\N改變龍脈方向的地方是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中禪寺湖的正下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.61,0:21:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 在山麓展開的湖泊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正好當接住氣的盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.32,0:21:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制五芒星的\N玉座之陣在哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.66,0:21:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水在戰場原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.03,0:21:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 秘密的機關\N也被他得到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翡翠紋章確實被掉換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但並不一定是靈水所為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.17,0:22:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之現在\N只能趕快趕往戰場原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.11,0:22:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔 你傷還沒好吧\N馬給你用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.82,0:22:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.75,0:22:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(咒)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.40,0:22:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人都不知不覺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們手掌心裏頭跳舞呢

